Wilson;; Photo, Terry Anne Jones and Wilson give each other a high-five after 
completing wreathes,; Photo, and Sharon Kuppermann and Susie Nack put the 
finishing touches on an infant's teddy bear quilt. The items will be sold at 
Cottage Co-op bazaar. KAREN TAPIA / Los Angeles Times 
