VILLAGE (CA) -- DEVELOPMENT AND REDEVELOPMENT; THOUSAND OAKS (CA) -- 
ANNEXATIONS; WESTLAKE VILLAGE (CA) -- INCORPORATION; LIFESTYLES; QUALITY OF 
LIFE 
</P>
